Academic Citation
If you use this code or its derivatives in your academic research or publications, we kindly request that you cite the following associated paper:

Bemis et al., (2024) A&A, 692, A146

Additional relevant works that provide foundational context for this code include:

Bemis & Wilson, (2023) ApJ, 945, 42

Sharda & Krumholz, (2022) MNRAS, 509, 1959

Your citation helps acknowledge the scientific work behind this software and supports its continued development.